sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant CLI
    participant AuditWorkflow
    participant ContextBuilder
    participant FS as FileSystem
    participant Claude as Claude LLM

    User->>CLI: audit [--scope all|specs|manual]
    CLI->>AuditWorkflow: runAuditWorkflow(scope)

    AuditWorkflow->>ContextBuilder: buildFilesContext()
    ContextBuilder->>FS: read playwright.config.ts
    FS-->>ContextBuilder: config content
    ContextBuilder->>FS: read .gitignore
    FS-->>ContextBuilder: gitignore content

    loop for each util (x7)
        ContextBuilder->>FS: read utils/*.ts (consoleGuard, navigation, cookies…)
        FS-->>ContextBuilder: util content
    end

    loop for each spec file
        ContextBuilder->>FS: read tests/**/*.spec.ts
        FS-->>ContextBuilder: spec content + specCount++
    end

    ContextBuilder-->>AuditWorkflow: { context, fileCount }

    AuditWorkflow->>Claude: auditTests(context)

    Note over Claude: Checks per file — imports, URLs,<br/>navigation, selectors, assertions,<br/>anti-patterns, config, gitignore,<br/>structure, global consistency

    Claude-->>AuditWorkflow: report (File · Line · Issue · Severity)

    AuditWorkflow->>AuditWorkflow: parseSummary() → errorCount, warningCount

    alt errorCount > 0
        AuditWorkflow-->>User: ❌ summary (errors / warnings) + exit(1)
    else
        AuditWorkflow-->>User: ✅ summary (warnings only) + exit(0)
    end
